Pytest - Unit testing framework

Advantages:
Parallel Execution
Run the test cases in groups
Skip
Very simple syntax
Conftest
Inbuild reporting

File name should either start/end with test
methodname also should start with test

Running the file
------------------
pytest -v

To print any statements
pytest -v -s
or
pytest -v --capture=no

To Run specific file
pytest filename -v -s
